N1Arxiv — dual licence

This repository ships content (papers, bundles) under a different licence
than its code (Hugo layouts, CI workflows, validator scripts, tests).
The split is intentional: the papers are scholarly works whose reuse
norms are governed by CC-BY-4.0; the platform code is permissively
licensed under MIT so other patient-centered preprint efforts can
fork it.

