================================================================
SECTION 3 — Resolving ambiguity
================================================================

If a file's licence is ambiguous (e.g., a tooling helper inside
`content/`), the more permissive licence (MIT) applies to the code
component and CC-BY-4.0 applies to any prose. When in doubt, open an
issue and the maintainers will clarify in a follow-up PR.
